data.description: Well maintained income generating corner triplex. Property features three one bedroom units and an enclosed one car garage.  Two units are occupied and one unit is vacant (3rd floor) giving the new owner the flexibility of occupying the premises or obtaining a tenant. All units are in good condition and feature a full bathroom. All utilities are separated. Excellent for an investor or owner occupant. Great location close to public transportation, major highways, shopping, and minutes to center city.  Motivated Seller. Property is being sold in As-Is condition.
